articles.title: Wallabies edge Japan in European warm-up for 5th straight win - News24
articles.description: Australia warmed up for their rugby tour of Europe with a nervy victory over Japan, the Wallabies' fifth successive Test win.
articles.content:
Australia warmed up for their rugby tour of Europe with a nervy 32-23 victory over Japan in Oita on Saturday, the Wallabies' fifth successive Test win.
